Title: This Is the Time for Silence
---
The beauty of the mountain is talked about most from a distance,

not while one is scaling the summit with life at risk. That is the time for
 silence, one-pointedness,

reflection, and drawing upon all your skills so you might return from the
 cloud's domain

and inspire others to breathe closer to God, while still human, the way you did
